Package: msdialr
Type: Package
Title: Post-process MS-DIAL results in R
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
  person("Carsten", "Jaeger", 
  email = "carsten.jaeger@bam.de", 
  role = c("aut", "cre"),
  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2192-1792"))
Description: This package provides functions for post-processing MS-DIAL (https://doi.org/10.1038/nmeth.3393) results in R. Import MS-DIAL alignment files, filter features, normalize intensities, and add annotation data from e.g. MS-FINDER, MSPepSearch and ClassyFire. Plot functions for mass spectra and chromatograms allow creating of simple QC plots.
